{"type": "article", "id": 26285, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-05-03T06:49:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 27043, "name": "JinGoo"}, {"id": 27044, "name": "Leather Ruck Sack"}, {"id": 27046, "name": "Foop"}, {"id": 27047, "name": "Zerobody"}, {"id": 27048, "name": "我爱瑜伽"}, {"id": 27060, "name": "Gardeniers"}, {"id": 27049, "name": "DAQI CONCEPT"}, {"id": 27050, "name": "Loyal Srticklin"}, {"id": 27052, "name": "Cestec"}, {"id": 27053, "name": "Cristiano Mino"}, {"id": 27054, "name": "非常建筑"}, {"id": 27061, "name": "Estudio Versus"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702152456p9sn6STMXcA85iWt.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">          </p>\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>间关 by 大器创意</h2>\n<p class=\"\">这个名为“间关”的家饰由来自台湾的产品设计团队<a href=\"http://daqiconcept.com/\">大器创意</a>（<a href=\"http://daqiconcept.com/\" target=\"_blank\">DAQI CONCEPT</a>）设计研发。“间关”一词在古代被用来形容宛转的鸟啼声，而在养鸟文化里，鸟笼就好像是文人雅士的必备家饰。大器将东方传统的家饰鸟笼概念和气氛灯光、蓝光音响结合在了一起，不仅可以作为家饰增添居家氛围，也是一个用音乐创造更好气氛的“歌唱鸟”。你可以在 <a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/jingoo-transform-your-space-with-music-and-light#/\">Indiegogo</a> 上了解更多信息，参与众筹的最低早鸟价为 179 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181525ptqkiNbRc9MZa7mQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181526bnFoSgjd9CI5KrHE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181526LRqmJ13SKPyikhZM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181527vlzsx4gjkBiOo71m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181527VTqKzsA6IdR3ljfo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181528z8DiKCm3N5Rxqavl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Leather Ruck Sack by Loyal Srticklin</h2>\n<p class=\"\">这个散发着复刻质感的皮革包名为 Leather Ruck Sack，是美国阿拉巴马州独立品牌 <a href=\"http://loyalstricklin.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Loyal Stricklin</a> 的一款产品。背包由植鞣真皮制作而成，坚固耐重的同时，恰到好处的褶皱为背包增添了时尚感，好像是电影中出现的户外探险家的装备。无论是打算来一场旅行还是想为日常生活增添一股户外风，都很合适。你可以通过<a href=\"http://loyalstricklin.com/products/leather-ruck-sack-light-tan\">预定链接</a>了解它的详细规格，售价为 750 美元，需要花费两周时间制作。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181528mjWxfvH9FlwasDL1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181528XKnMI1Upl9RQb8L2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071815298XMfIOxAhp3YHaTv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181529Td3BXfmHaEJtMnYj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Foop by Cestec<span style=\"background-color: transparent;\"><br></span>\n</h2>\n<p class=\"\">日本的 Cestec 公司推出的这款名为 Foop 的水耕工作台是一个有着未来感的智能小菜园。Foop 内可以种植各类不高于 25 厘米的蔬菜，将种子和海绵放进栽培杯中，加入水和肥料耐心等待即可。通过配套的 app 你可以随时了解蔬菜的状态，比如还有几天成熟、是否还需要加水等。它的售价为 38800 日元，限量 100 台的首批预订已经截止，你可以通过它的<a href=\"https://foop.cestec.jp/\">官方网站</a>了解更多信息。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060718153039gkBusNOFDEro1l.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181531Udn10swmB9NpFvLM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.43375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181531JAN5V3qa2M1mEtRf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181531w3JjLU1ucPZfrGQF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071815321mkdentRAZGNiO68.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071815328UNs4kJaezAhZpO1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Zerobody by Cristiano Mino</h2>\n<p class=\"\">Zerobody 是由 spa 设计公司 <a href=\"http://www.starpool.com/\" onclick=\"__gaTracker('send', 'event', 'outbound-article', 'http://www.starpool.com/', 'Starpool');\" target=\"_blank\">Starpool</a> 和脑健康研究公司 <a href=\"http://www.neocogita.com/en/\" onclick=\"__gaTracker('send', 'event', 'outbound-article', 'http://www.neocogita.com/en/', 'Neocogita');\" target=\"_blank\">Neocogita</a> 共同推出的一款加热的水床。平躺在上面的时候，能够体会到漂浮的感觉，所以也被称为“干水池”（dry pool）。在“漂浮”的过程中，人体内产生的脑内啡会压抑疼痛信号的传递，使人感到欣快。除此之外，配套的 <a href=\"http://www.nurelax.com/en/\" onclick=\"__gaTracker('send', 'event', 'outbound-article', 'http://www.nurelax.com/en/', 'NU RELAX');\" target=\"_blank\">NU RELAX</a> 提供专门为此设计的冥想环节，你可以通过收听音频来让身体彻底放松。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181533PIbV8ApmaXLCHweS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181533nPXNiAMS2G7yCJ8h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181534L4mKUyg2SeNjnlxa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181534bXcfj0y2CUT1M7np.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.88\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071815354HFzurThp0KOYeaS.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.81\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181535FBATK4dvPfSmnrwu.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>我爱瑜伽 by 非常建筑</h2>\n<p class=\"\">这套名为“我爱瑜伽”的家具由设计师张永和其带领的建筑设计事务所<a href=\"http://www.fcjz.com/\">非常建筑</a>和<a href=\"http://qmrd-life.com/\">曲美家居</a>携手打造，目前在上海当代艺术博物馆举行的<a href=\"http://www.powerstationofart.com/cn/exhibition/detail/f2bgxA.html\">“建筑之名 非常建筑泛设计展”</a>上展出。曲木工艺为设计创造了更大的弹性，“我爱瑜伽”系列中的每一件家具都由单独一块曲木制成。不依靠其他素材，而是以一种非常自然的方式联结的方式透露着淡定和优雅的气质。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071815361OeIqFWbClt2Ka0T.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62958435\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181537d0QV2G7Lpa1DCJn6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68215159\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181537g5RtZM4ryhCBVXdY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74205379\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181538SOANEQm3rb7B5iwc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68826406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181538N8OlMdYK9ACfGgjn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.01833741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181538lEBcw9gInPkZrdsD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.93765281\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Gardeniers by Estudio Versus</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://estudioverus.com/\">Estudio Versus</a> 为 Gardeniers 的橄榄油所设计的包装不同于常规的那些可以看到橄榄油的透明玻璃瓶，让人眼前一亮。它白色的瓶身看上去有些纤细，搭配金色的文字带给人一种高端的感觉。若不是瓶身上绘制精美的蔬菜图片，你或许很难将它同橄榄油联系起来。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181539NGjwByuVtlzKa2Of.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.644\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181539wqt9kpbMhNHK6gX8.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.357\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071815405ZVhXgDRI9lSs1YN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.636\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181540MHvCRctV9T17aLf5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181541HsCBzN7Ohy14Qkou.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.701\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}